    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In the western Christian liturgical calendar, the first Sunday after Pentecost; in eastern Christianity, the Sunday of Pentecost. Instituted to honor the Holy Trinity: the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
